---
layout: base.njk
title: Hesed Psychotherapy International
---
<section class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">Psychotherapy • Transactional Analysis • Resilience</p>
  <h1>Helping people understand their inner world and rebuild healthier ways of living.</h1>
  <p>Hesed Psychotherapy International supports individuals, couples, families and organisations through psychotherapy, counselling, career coaching and workplace mental health programmes.</p>
  <a class="button" href="#booking">Book a Session</a>
</section>

<section id="insights" class="section">
  <p class="eyebrow">Insights</p>
  <h2>Latest Articles</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    {% for article in collections.articles %}
    <a class="card" href="{{ article.url }}">
      <span>{{ article.data.category }}</span>
      <h3>{{ article.data.title }}</h3>
      <p>{{ article.data.excerpt }}</p>
      <small>{{ article.date | readableDate if false }}{{ article.data.date }} · {{ article.data.readTime }}</small>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section id="booking" class="section cta">
  <h2>Ready to begin?</h2>
  <p>Book a session or reach out to explore how psychotherapy can support your next step.</p>
  <a class="button" href="mailto:jumh.tantri@gmail.com">Contact Me</a>
</section>
